Package wogwt.translatable.rpc

Interface Summary
WOGWTClientEO The primary interface for DTOs that can be transferred to the client.
WOGWTSerializableEO Adds a method to EOEnterpriseObject to return a clientSnapshot dictionary that can be used to populate a DTO object to return EO data to the client.
 

Class Summary
AlertOnErrorAsyncCallback<T> An AsyncCallback that displays an alert for any error.
DialogOnErrorAsyncCallback<T> An AsyncCallback that displays a modal ErrorDialog for any error.
LogOnErrorAsyncCallback<T> An AsyncCallback that does Log.error for any error.
RPCUtil Utility functions for use with RPC on the server.
WOGWTClientEOImpl Base class for the client DTO objects used in place of EOs.
